                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-0000006fe32d05-6ba0-48e7-91fc-04b256d98a1a" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(tan\ {θ}=\frac{Psin\ {α}}{P+Pcos\ {α}}⇒tan\ {θ}=\frac{sin\ {α}}{1+cos\ {α}}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000016fe32d05-6ba0-48e7-91fc-04b256d98a1a"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000006fe32d05-6ba0-48e7-91fc-04b256d98a1a {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000016fe32d05-6ba0-48e7-91fc-04b256d98a1a {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000008b4a0113-e95c-4c57-8fdc-48b9d09472cd" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(⇒tan\ {θ}=\frac{2sin\ {\frac{α}{2}cos\ {\frac{α}{2}}}}{2{cos}^{2}\ {\frac{α}{2}}}⇒tan\ {θ}=tan\ {\frac{α}{2}}∴θ=\frac{α}{2}\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000018b4a0113-e95c-4c57-8fdc-48b9d09472cd"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000008b4a0113-e95c-4c57-8fdc-48b9d09472cd {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000018b4a0113-e95c-4c57-8fdc-48b9d09472cd {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000005717c36a-79d1-438c-8f70-5fceda7cbce2" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="pt-0000015717c36a-79d1-438c-8f70-5fceda7cbce2">weK&#237;</span><span class="pt-0000025717c36a-79d1-438c-8f70-5fceda7cbce2">:</span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000035717c36a-79d1-438c-8f70-5fceda7cbce2"> </span><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(α=θ+θ=2θ⇒θ=\frac{α}{2}\) </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000005717c36a-79d1-438c-8f70-5fceda7cbce2 {line-he